.PP
.BR [global]
.RS
.TP
pool\-name
Pool identifier
.TP
journal\-path
Journal file location
.TP
metadata\-path
Metadata file location
.TP
snapshot\-interval\-hours
Periodic metadata snapshot interval (0 to disable)
.RE
.PP
.BR [server]
.RS
.TP
socket\-path
Client socket path
.TP
admin\-socket\-path
Admin socket path
.TP
require\-root\-user
Require root for connections (bool)
.TP
read\-timeout\-seconds
Connection read timeout
.TP
idle\-timeout\-seconds
Connection idle timeout
.TP
max\-timeout\-ms
Max per-request timeout
.RE
.PP
.BR [limits]
.RS
.TP
max\-request\-size\-bytes
Max request size
.TP
max\-write\-size\-bytes
Max write size
.TP
write\-rate\-limit\-per\-second
Write rate limit
.TP
write\-burst
Write burst size
.TP
read\-rate\-limit\-per\-second
Read rate limit
.TP
read\-burst
Read burst size
.TP
max\-goroutines
Max concurrent goroutines
.TP
slow\-query\-threshold\-ms
Slow query warning threshold
.RE
.PP
.BR [logging]
.RS
.TP
level
Log level (debug, info, warn, error)
.TP
json
JSON logging format (bool)
.RE
.PP
.BR [audit]
.RS
.TP
enabled
Enable audit logging (bool)
.TP
path
Audit log file path
.RE
.PP
.BR [alert]
.RS
.TP
enabled
Enable alert webhooks (bool)
.TP
url
Webhook URL
.RE
.PP
.BR [scrub]
.RS
.TP
enabled
Enable automatic scrub (bool)
.TP
interval\-hours
Scrub interval
.TP
